Source: aurex-virtualbox
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Luis Antonio Garcia Gisbert <luisgg@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0)
Standards-Version: 3.8.4

Package: aurex-virtualbox-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, aurex-cache
Description: generic virtualbox metapackage for aurex
 This package installs common stuff for aurex-virtualbox
 metapackages.

Package: aurex-virtualbox-5.0
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, virtualbox-5.0, aurex-virtualbox-common (=${binary:Version})
Description: generic virtualbox-5.0 metapackage for aurex
 This package allow automatic download and installation of
 extension packs on virtualbox updates.

Package: aurex-virtualbox-4.3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, virtualbox-4.3 (=4.3.32-103443~Ubuntu~raring) [amd64], virtualbox-4.3 (=4.3.32-103443~Ubuntu~precise) [i386], aurex-virtualbox-common (=${binary:Version})
Description: generic virtualbox-4.3 metapackage for aurex
 This package allow automatic download and installation of
 extension packs on virtualbox updates.

Package: aurex-virtualbox-4.2
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, virtualbox-4.2 (=4.2.24-92790~Ubuntu~precise), aurex-virtualbox-common (=${binary:Version})
Description: generic virtualbox-4.2 metapackage for aurex
 This package will always depend on the latest virtualbox-4.2 and
 extension pack available to keep both programs in sync.

Package: aurex-virtualbox-4.1
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, virtualbox-4.1 (=4.1.26-84997~Ubuntu~precise), aurex-virtualbox-common (=${binary:Version})
Description: generic virtualbox-4.1 metapackage for aurex
 This package will always depend on the latest virtualbox-4.1 and
 extension pack available to keep both programs in sync.
